"title": "1050: God, goodness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1050",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All God's perfect qualities are made freely available to all for the benefit of the whole world.</p>\n<h2>God alone is good</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:18\">MRK 10:18</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:17\">MAT 19:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:19\">LUK 18:19</a></p>\n<h2>God demonstrates his goodness</h2>\n<h3>In his actions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:68\">PSA 119:68</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:18\">2CH 30:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20\">NEH 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:1\">PSA 73:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:10\">PSA 143:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:4\">ROM 2:4</a></p>\n<h3>In his work of creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:4\">1TI 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:4\">GEN 1:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:31\">GEN 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:9\">PSA 145:9</a></p>\n<h3>In his love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:5\">PSA 86:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:34\">1CH 16:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:1\">PSA 106:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:7-Ps25:8\">PSA 25:7–25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps69:16\">PSA 69:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps100:5\">PSA 100:5</a></p>\n<h3>In his gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:17\">JAS 1:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num13:27\">NUM 13:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:7\">DEU 8:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:11\">DEU 26:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:11\">HEB 9:11</a></p>\n<h3>In his promises</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:14-Josh23:15\">JOS 23:14–23:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:28\">2SA 7:28</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:26\">1CH 17:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:56\">1KI 8:56</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:10\">JER 29:10</a></p>\n<h3>In his commands</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:39\">PSA 119:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7\">PSA 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:12\">ROM 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:16\">ROM 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:2\">ROM 12:2</a></p>\n<h2>God's goodness is to be experienced</h2>\n<h3>God is good to those who trust him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:8\">PSA 34:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:7\">NAM 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:19\">EXO 33:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:10\">2CH 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job42:11\">JOB 42:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:19-Ps31:20\">PSA 31:19–31:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:11\">PSA 84:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:17\">PSA 86:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:25\">LAM 3:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:14-Amos5:15\">AMO 5:14–5:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:3\">1PE 2:3</a></p>\n<h3>God's people can rely on his goodness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:40\">JER 32:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:6\">PSA 23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:13\">PSA 27:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:11\">MAT 7:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:13\">LUK 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:6\">PHP 1:6</a></p>\n<h2>God works positively for good in unfavourable circumstances</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:20\">GEN 50:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23-Acts2:24\">ACT 2:23–2:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:28\">ROM 8:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:17\">2CO 4:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:10\">HEB 12:10</a></p>\n<h2>God's goodness is to be praised</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps135:3\">PSA 135:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:10\">DEU 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:13\">2CH 5:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr7:3\">2CH 7:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:5\">PSA 86:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:1\">PSA 136:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:7\">PSA 145:7</a></p>",
